Class AddressBook

java.lang.Object
com.project1.AddressBook
public class AddressBook
extends java.lang.Object
Class that holds a collection of objects of the class AddressEntry Contains the methods to perform operations against the AddressEntry collection such as add, remove, readFromFile, list, find, and getAddressEntry
